‚úÖ If you actually meant Java (not JavaScript)

Here‚Äôs a Java console program that displays portfolio info:

public class Portfolio {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("===== My Portfolio =====");
        System.out.println("Name: John Doe");
        System.out.println("Profession: Web Developer");
        System.out.println("\n--- About Me ---");
        System.out.println("I am passionate about building interactive and modern web applications.");
        System.out.println("\n--- Projects ---");
        System.out.println("1. Portfolio Website");
        System.out.println("2. E-commerce App");
        System.out.println("3. Chat Application");
        System.out.println("\n--- Contact ---");
        System.out.println("Email: johndoe@example.com");
    }
}


